  <name>BrowserOS</name>
  <summary>The open-source Agentic browser powered by AI</summary>
  <description>
    <p>BrowserOS is an innovative web browser that integrates AI agents directly into your browsing experience. Built on Chromium, it provides advanced AI-powered features while maintaining compatibility with existing web technologies.</p>
    <p>Key features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>AI-powered web assistance and automation</li>
      <li>Model Context Protocol (MCP) server integration</li>
      <li>Built-in agent framework for web interactions</li>
      <li>Privacy-focused design with sandboxing</li>
      <li>Modern Chromium-based rendering engine</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This is a community package of BrowserOS and not officially supported by BrowserOS AI.</p>
  </description>
