      <description>
        <p>BrowserOS - v0.33.0</p>
        <ul>
          <li>**OpenAI-compatible provider support** — You can now connect any OpenAI-compatible API endpoint in providers.</li>
          <li>**Multi-window &amp; multi-profile agent support** — Agent now works smoothly across multiple windows and browser profiles, with affinity to the profile/window where it was started.</li>
